Title: Good Trouble fans, it’s returning!
Narrative:
How will Mariana and the group begin the next stage of their transition to working as young adults in Los Angeles? An American drama television programme called Good Trouble. 

Webnews special reported that it is an offshoot of The Fosters on Freeform. However, with four seasons already under its belt and audience interest at an all-time high, the question is whether or not the recently released series will be able to continue for further seasons. 

The network's choice to renew the series for a second season after this positive reception from the viewers was an easy one given the reviews. We've put up a concise synopsis of everything you need to know about the season's release date, storyline, and cast members to assist you in getting ready before watching the new season.

Your good news is that Good Trouble is returning for a fifth season. It comes ahead of the finale of Season 4 of The Fosters spinoff, which runs through August.
